column5: Hi everyone,  Just wanted to post the catch for opener weekend
Is that a small brown at the bottom?
Yep small brown at the bottom, he was bigger then it looks in the picture... tasted quite delicious I might add too..
Nice haul,   Didn't you know it's not good to let the fish flop in the leafs before you put it in the frying pan!    Just kidding around of course.
Steelhead with a side of mud, mmmmmmmmmm.
Some beauty fish there, well done
I'd say your opener was a success! Nice job.
wow great job better luck than me lol
wow great job better luck than me lol   5 times as lucky as me.................er, um....wait a minute 5 times 0 is still 0!
